dcterms:description: A comprehensive dataset for network intrusion detection systems, containing real normal and synthetic abnormal network traffic generated in the synthetic environment of the University of New South Wales (UNSW) cyber security lab. The dataset is characterized by 9 attack families and normal traffic generated over two distinct capture days.
dcterms:title: UNSW15 dataset
